    <body>
      <section eId="sec_304_A">
        <num>304-A</num>
        <heading>Electronic service of process</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_304_A__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>\nelectronic service of process authorized by the provisions of this\nchapter is an optional program at no additional cost to the user;</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_304_A__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>\nany corporation subject to the laws of this chapter will continue to\nreceive service of process by mail unless such corporation notifies the\nsecretary of an affirmative choice to receive service of process by way\nof the program through electronic means, in which case digital copies\nwill be made accessible but paper documents will not be mailed; and</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_304_A__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>\nsuch choice may be reversed by the corporation at any time and,\nthereafter, service by mail will resume.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
